#CybOX v2.0.1 XML --> OVAL XML Generation Script                       #
#Generates OVAL 5.7 definitions/tests/objects from CyBOX v2.0.1 XML    #
#                                                               	   #
#Compatible with content produced using CybOX v1.0 draft               #
